# Step 1:
Once docker is installed, make login with below command from command line.
docker login

# Step 2:
Pull the latest image of docker, using below command.
docker pull centos

# Step 3:
Create shared folder in your laptop.
Example : Create directory “shared” under [D drive]
  
# Step 4:
Make git clone and download all these code to your local machine.

# Step 5:
Once share directory is created, please modify it in docker file.

# Step 6:
Navigate to the directory where file is downloaded and run below command.
docker build -t centos-with-ssh .
